  "type": "EPCISDocument",
  "schemaVersion": "2.0",
  "creationDate": "2026-04-15T10:00:00.000Z",
  "_comment_architecture": [
    "EUDR Exemption Declaration — reference pattern for GSMP WR 25-252 / WR 26-122.",
    "",
    "GS1 alignment status (2026-04-17): GS1 EUDR Provisional Standard Release P",
    "(Sep 2025) defines NO exemption terms. The 13 April 2026 GS1 EUDR MSWG",
    "previewed a planned gs1:regulatoryExemption model that would replace",
    "gs1:regulatoryIdentifier when an exemption applies; that model is not yet",
    "published. This example uses the eudr:-namespaced reference pattern that",
    "mirrors the planned semantics. See eudr/docs/GS1_ALIGNMENT.md.",
    "",
    "masterDataAvailableFor contains ONLY gs1: properties (regulatoryIdentifier",
    "is correctly OMITTED from the regulatoryInformation block here — an exemption",
    "replaces it per WR 25-252 / MSWG 2026-04-13).",
    "ALL exemption properties (eudr:, dpp:) are at EVENT level.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,eudr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/eudr/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
  "_scenario": "A downstream operator (Waldwirtschaft Schmidt GmbH) declares a temporary exemption for a specific batch of European Oak round wood, asserting that the batch originated from already-verified low-risk sources per EUDR Article 2.17 (downstream operator simplified due diligence). The exemption is scoped to batch LOT-2026-Q1-0042 and valid from 2026-04-15 to 2026-07-15.",
