  "_notes": {
    "eancom_equivalence": "In EANCOM syntax this exemption would be carried as IMD segment C272:DE7081='TEMPORARY_EXEMPTION' + C273:DE7009 with reason code 'DOWNSTREAM_VERIFIED_LOW_RISK'. The batch scope LOT-2026-Q1-0042 would appear in GIN segment under SG22. See WR 25-252 for the full EANCOM solution.",
    "gs1xml_equivalence": "The equivalent GS1 XML structure is defined in WR 25-252 (eBallot).",
    "gdsn_equivalence": "The equivalent GDSN master data structure is defined in WR 26-122 (Community Review).",
    "status": "Reference pattern; the EANCOM/XML/GDSN specifications are authoritative. This EPCIS JSON-LD example demonstrates the equivalent semantics for projects using EPCIS as their data sharing layer."
